hr.fer.zemris.java.tecaj.hw5.db

Class StudentDatabase

  • java.lang.Object
    • hr.fer.zemris.java.tecaj.hw5.db.StudentDatabase

  • public class StudentDatabase
extends java.lang.Object
    Database implementation that holds StudentRecords. It offers 2 methods: first for fetching records in O(1) with known JMBAG, and second for filtering with given IFilter.
    Author:
    Dan
